ate four hours to kill alias mary dow the glass key three smart girls next time we love the return of sophie lang the big broadcast of the jungle princess bulldog drummond escapes wings over honolulu easy living ebb tide wise girl her jungle love tropic holiday men with wings say it in french hotel imperial beau geste everything happens at night french without tears irene the doctor takes a wife arise my love untamed i wanted wings skylark the lady has plans reap the wild wind are husbands necessary the major and the minor star spangled rhythm forever and a day the crystal ball lady in the dark the uninvited till we meet again ministry of fear kitty the lost weekend the well groomed bride california the imperfect lady the trouble with women golden earrings variety girl cameo the big clock so evil my love sealed verdict miss tatlock s millions cameo alias nick beal it happens every spring a woman of distinction a life of her own copper canyon close to my heart circle of danger night into morning rhubarb bugles in the afternoon something to live for the thief jamaica run let s do it again dial m for murder the girl in the red velvet swing a man alone also director high flight lisbon also director and associate producer three brave men the river s edge the safecracker the premature burial panic in year zero also director x the man with the x ray eyes the confession red roses for the fuhrer hostile witness love story embassy the big game frogs the thing with two heads columbo the greenhouse jungle the student connection the house in nightmare park terror in the wax museum gold escape to witch mountain the million dollar fire the swiss conspiracy aces high the last tycoon the girl in yellow pajamas the uncanny slavers blackout oliver s story a game for vultures survival run the attic the sea serpent cyfeiriadau dolennau allanol classic movies ray milland categori actorion cymreig categori genedigaethau categori marwolaethau categori pobl o gastell nedd categori ymfudwyr 